 Sorry for the delay. Had to finish an other project.

 ensuring that the behaviour in the normal case stays the same, one is a
 minimal example of the problem and the third one is a proper test case

 am not sure if the cla/google check will pass. I tried to rebase it but I
 am not sure that helps.

 Thank you!
